orts  entertainmentwashington dche served as chairman of revolution money a digital and online payments strategy company that was acquired by american express earlier this year and where he continues to serve as an adviser from  he held numerous senior positions with aol most recently as vice chairman he previously was president of redgate communications corp which was acquired by aol in  also is a director of nutrisystem inc fourth quarteradded to nutrisystem inc  fort washington panutrisystem markets dieting products revenues are  million theodore j leonsis executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    pm et media company overview of monumental sports  entertainment llc snapshotpeople  overviewboard memberscommittees executive profile theodore j leonsis founder owner chairman and chief executive officer  monumental sports  entertainment llcagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industriessee board relationships background mr theodore j leonsis also known as ted is the founder and chairman of viewlift inc mr leonsis is the founder and owner of monumental sports  entertainment llc and serves as its chairman and chief executive officer mr leonsis is the founder of revolution llc he serves as a founder and partner at revolution growth he serves as a founder at the firm since  he served as managing partner of revolution growth he serves as senior advisor at rre ventures  llc he founded snagfilms inc in  and serves as its chairman he serves as an advisor of launchbox digital he founded lincoln holdings llc in may  he served as a strategic advisor at mobile posse inc he served as the president and vice chairman of audience business at historic aol llc until january   mr leonsis served as an interim cochief executive officer at groupon inc from february   to august   he served as an advisor of time warner inc since december   he served as the president of the advanced systems group at time warner inc he served as special advisor of two harbors investment corp since october  he was the founder of redgate communications corporation where he is credited with having coined the phrase new media he served as the president and chief executive officer of redgate communications corporation he was employed at aol from november  to december  he served as the president of interactive properties group at time warner inc from march  to january  he served as the president of america online studios from november  to march  vice chairman and president of aol core services and president of aol web properties he served as president of america online services company also a division of time warner inc from  to  mr leonsis served as a strategist and visionary of historic aol llc he was a mentor to dozens of successful aol executives mr leonsis was known as aols champion of the member and was responsible for delivering a worldclass experience for aols members in todays multiband environment he oversaw the core aol service and led efforts to develop cuttingedge products and programming across its narrowband broadband wireless and voice services and oversaw efforts to capitalize on growth opportunities in advertising search and commerce currently he serves as a coexecutive chairman of axiomatic esports he has been chairman of lincoln holdings llc since may  mr leonsis serves as the vice chairman of dc  fedbid inc and potomac school futures campaign he serves on the board of bedrock manufacturing he has been a lead independent director of groupon inc since november   he has been an independent director of groupon inc since june  and american express company since july  he has been a member of us advisory board at sportradar ag since october   he has been a director of fedbid inc since january   he serves as a director of resonate networks inc mevio inc customink llc optoro inc clearspring technologies inc and georgetown university mr leonsis serves on the board of governors for the nba and nhl he served as the chairman of addthis llc he served as the chairman of clearspring technologies inc and fedbid inc since january   mr leonsis served as chairman of serve virtual enterprises inc he served as the chairman of groupon inc from august   to november   he served as vice chairman at groupon inc from april  to august   he served as vice chairman of historic aol llc alternate name aol llc until december   and also served as its vice chairman emeritus mr leonsis served as a director of rosetta stone uk limited and mediabank llc he served as a director of bridgevine inc since february  proxicom inc since  and preview travel inc since june  mr leonsis served as an independent director of rosetta stone inc from december   to may   and nutrisystem inc from december   to june   he served as the mayor of orchid florida through his leonsis foundation he is active in supporting such organizations as hoop dreams best buddies youthaids see forever foundation and venture philanthropy partners mr leonsis is a pioneer of the internet and new media a sports team owner and an innovator in the world of philanthropy he participated in launches of the apple macintosh the ibm pc and wang office automation and founded four computing magazines mr leonsis is the producer of three documentaries feature nanking kicking it and a fighting chance his book the business of happiness  secrets to extraordinary success in work and life was published in february  he has been named one of the  most powerful people in sports by sporting news and businessman of the year by washington business journal one of the  most influential people in sports and one of the top  entrepreneur of the year mr leonsis holds a ba in american studies from georgetown university in  and a graduate of lowell high in read full background corporate headquarters  f street nwwashington district of columbia united statesphone fax  board members memberships directorgeorgetown universitydirectormevio incdi